Class "RMQ_n_1_improved" in files "RMQ_n_1_improved.[c|h]pp" implements
the representation of RMQ information as described in the paper:

"Theoretical and Prcatical Imprevements on the RMQ-problem, with Appli-
cations to LCA and LCA",  CPM'06,  LNCS 4009,  pp. 36--48,  by Johannes
Fischer and Volker Heun.

Type "make" to get an executable "testRMQ" which, when run, creates
a random array of length 3,000,000  and runs some tests.

